{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2734380/extras/walking_village_cropped.gif?t=1734866605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mushroom Kid's Big Grass Sword</strong> is a narrative, physics-based, precision platformer that follows <strong>Mica</strong>, a little mushroom, on a journey to rescue their village after the residents are captured by a gigantic bird. Meet Grandmashroom as she leads Mica to a mysterious temple to claim the Blade of Grass: a powerful weapon with the ability to pull Mica up ledges and over dangerous obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2734380/extras/temple_first_obstacle_cropped.gif?t=1734866605\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Blade of Grass</strong> is a unique weapon that <strong>can be rotated at any angle the player desires</strong>, allowing Mica to be pulled over obstacles. Combining this with Mica's jumping and gliding abilities creates a platforming experience like no other. Mica must time his jumps and angle the blade to overcome challenges and traverse a mystical world, meeting several wacky mushrooms and growing the sword to comical lengths along the way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wield the Blade of Grass!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Master a unique move-set!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meet funny characters throughout your journey!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Mushrooms... lots of mushrooms...</strong>\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44\ud83c\udf44</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2734380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734866605